snippet.title: Windblown Early Access Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
The Vortex nears... 

Windblown launches into Steam Early Access on the 24th of October! Dash your way to greatness in this lightning-fast action roguelite for 1-3 players. 

Absorb the powers of fallen warriors and bring total carnage to the pesky sentinels that stand in your way! 

Jump into the Single Player Demo on October 14th during the upcoming Steam Next Fest, where you progress will carry over into the main game!

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1911610/Windblown/

Follow us on Social:  
X: https://twitter.com/windblowngame  
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@windblowngame  
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/windblowngame/

Music by Danger 
 - YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@2emedanger 
 - Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/2emedanger/ 
 - Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/intl-fr/artist/2o3U0ld93tHYowkoari4Vi
